byline.contributor: Ian Austen contributed reporting from Ottawa.

lead_paragraph: The violence began when a patrol was sent to check on reports of a house on fire. Gunmen then attacked a police station in the city.

headline.main: Gunmen in Jordan Kill 10, Including 7 Officers and a Canadian Tourist
headline.print_headline: Gunmen Kill 10, Including Tourist, in Jordan
